{"tid":1832534,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"穆迪將匯豐銀行及恒生(00011.HK)外幣存款評級由Aa2級降至Aa3級","createTime":"2020-01-21T08:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T02:14:14.000Z","uid":95138,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"76acb490bcbd36247633da2754cd8c1a150ca953","tid":1832534,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:42:49.000Z","msg":"穆迪將香港上海滙豐銀行及恒生銀行(<a href=\"http://00011.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00011.HK&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6qjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=b48e39ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00011.HK</a>)的長期外幣存款評級由Aa2級降至Aa3級，同時亦將其長期外幣銀行存款評級展望由「負面」調整至「穩定」。<br />\n<br />\n該行指出下調匯控及恒生外幣銀行存款評級主要基於該行將香港評級由Aa2級降至Aa3級，認為兩家銀行的外幣存款評級受制於香港的外幣存款限制。穆迪指兩家銀行本地存款評級展望亦為「負面」，相信評級難獲上調，假如兩家銀行能在未來12-18個月，即使面對香港經濟下行及經濟前景不確定，仍能維持強勁的資產質素及盈利能力，相信評級展望則有望可回復至「穩定」。<br />\n<br />\n如香港評級獲上調，銀行的外幣存款評級亦有機會獲上調。(el/t)"},{"pid":"4cbfecacc16db020101ef0c48805663d4929f082","tid":1832534,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:44:54.000Z","msg":"Source: AASTOCKS"},{"pid":"80cda498e6df26c124f1cd89afab52d5466ff28b","tid":1832534,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"冇錢了"},{"pid":"8cfacf89673b21538a2441bfb0f1bdfe836578d9","tid":1832534,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c1b687f7521f0592752b691deca67070caf489","tid":1832534,"uid":284855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"h